Full-Stack Developer with 3+ years of experience looking for a full time position
80% - backend Java development, 20% - frontend React development
Phone:  Birth year: 1991
E-mail:  Residence: Rehovot.
Linkedin: Nikita Doroshenko Languages: English, Hebrew, Russian.
TECHNICAL SKILLS
Programming languages: Java, JavaScript, TypeScript. Web: HTML 5, CSS 3, Bootstrap 5.
Technologies: OOP, AOP, Java Collection, Java Stream API, Rest, Maven, Project Lombok, Spring MVC,
Spring Framework(Spring Boot, Spring Web, Data MongoDB, Spring Cloud Stream, Spring Security, Spring
Starter Mail, Spring Validation), Awaitility, Mockito, MongoEmbedded, Hibernate, Apache Tomcat, Kafka,
Multithreading, Docker, Heroku, JPA, ORM, MongoDB Atlas, Junit, React, Redux.
Environments-IDE/Tools: Eclipse, Intellij IDEA, Visual Studio Code, GitHub, Postman, DBeaver.
Databases: MySQL, PostgreSQL, No SQL(MongoDB), H2 OS: Windows, Linux.
PROFESSIONAL HISTORY
2021  now Full-Stack Developer, Inetex (Rehovot , Israel)
Main project: Developing a service network for CV with microservices architecture.
Responsibilities:
 Participating in development of several services: employer service, cv service, security
service, schedule;
 Implementation of new functionality, work with MongoDB (geo search, aggregation
query);
 Integrating developed services into application (notification service);
 Implementation of frontend functionality (register, change password, update
employee data, routes);
 Writing and running Junit tests, refactoring code and fixing bugs;
Technologies: Java, JavaScript, TypeScript, Java Stream API, Spring boot, Spring Web, Spring
Data MongoDb, Spring Security, React, Redux, MongoDB, Junit, Rest.
2019  2021 Java Backend Developer, Miratorg (Belgorod, Russia)
Main project: Production reporting automation
Responsibilities:
 Installing and maintaining database;
 Populating a database with new information or transfer existing data into it;
 Creation and implementation of methods for working with data for the planning department;
Technologies: Java, Java Stream API, Spring web, Spring Data MongoDB, Junit, MongoDb, Docker.
2014  2019 Data Analyst, Miratorg (Belgorod, Russia)
Responsibilities:
 Developing and implementing reports;
 Collecting and adding data from various sources;
 Database support. (Adding, deleting data);
Technologies: Microsoft Excel, Visual Basic for Applications, Power BI, SQL, CSB, NAV, SAP.
EDUCATION
2008  2013 Applied Information Science in Economics
The Federal State Budget Educational Institution of Higher Education Baikal State University
2021 Special program for software developers' adaptation in accordance with Israel IT
technologies by Ministry of Absorption and Jewish Agency of Israel.
Tel Ran Educational Center
